snippet.description:
Jack Ma Life Changing Quotes. Jack Ma Yun is a Chinese business magnate, investor and philanthropist. He is the co-founder and former executive chairman of Alibaba Group, a multinational technology conglomerate. In addition, he co-founded Yunfeng Capital, a private equity firm. Ma is a strong proponent of an open and market-driven economy.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Jack Ma. The best quotes and aphorisms of Jack Ma that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Jack Ma are definitely worth your time.
